Package org.threadly.concurrent.wrapper.traceability

Wrappers for improving handling thread renaming during specific task (or wrapped pools) are executed.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ThreadRenamingExecutorWrapper
    Class which wraps a Executor and wraps all supplied tasks in a ThreadRenamingRunnableWrapper.
    ThreadRenamingRunnableWrapper
    A simple runnable wrapper which will rename the thread during execution, and set the name back at the end of execution.
    ThreadRenamingSchedulerServiceWrapper
    Class which wraps a SchedulerService and wraps all supplied tasks in a ThreadRenamingRunnableWrapper.
    ThreadRenamingSubmitterSchedulerWrapper
    Class which wraps a SubmitterScheduler and wraps all supplied tasks in a ThreadRenamingRunnableWrapper.
